Sentencas: The porous YSZ film was prepared by aqueous tape casting and the YSZ electrolyte film was prepared by organic tape casting.
Titulo: Performance of Iron-Based Anode Catalysts for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The porous YSZ-compact YSZ film composite was prepared via the stack pressure co-firing of the porous YSZ film and YSZ electrolyte film.
Titulo: Performance of Iron-Based Anode Catalysts for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The impregnated anode SOFC single cell was prepared by chemical impregnation method with the solution of ferric nitrate, cobalt nitrate and nickel nitrate which was impregnated in porous YSZ layer of the composite matrix.
Titulo: Performance of Iron-Based Anode Catalysts for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The performance of iron-based anode catalysts was studied, and the electrical properties of different anode SOFC single cells at different temperatures were tested and the morphology of the anode was observed by SEM.
Titulo: Performance of Iron-Based Anode Catalysts for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The anti-carbon performance of Co-YSZ and Ni-YSZ anode single cell was tested and compared.
Titulo: Performance of Iron-Based Anode Catalysts for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Results show that the catalytic activity of cobalt in the hydrogen atmosphere is the highest, the nickel is the second, and the iron is the worst.
Titulo: Performance of Iron-Based Anode Catalysts for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The catalytic activity of cobalt in alcohol atmosphere is still better than that of nickel, and the anti-carbon performance of Co-YSZ anode single cell is much better than that of Ni-YSZ single cell.
Titulo: Performance of Iron-Based Anode Catalysts for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The catalytic activity and the anti-carbon performance of cobalt in iron-based catalyst are best.
Titulo: Performance of Iron-Based Anode Catalysts for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
